{"tid":1596603,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗爭目標】又問收唔收貨","createTime":"2019-09-26T14:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T14:46:07.000Z","uid":158672,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d35f5cef2e549d13d9c9ef05c5558d95b6b8f7d2","tid":1596603,"uid":158672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:36:35.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"color: green;\">我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？</span></ins><br />\n缺一不可 係一個都不能少<br />\n次次政府表態 一定有人問有獨立調查收唔收貨<br />\n都話缺一不可 仲要問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">制度一直腐敗 日後會有更多人流血 距離民主自由愈黎愈遠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: green;\">懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考</span></ins><br />\n好多人都講左我地係要劍指政府 唔好停留於黑警仇恨 獨立調查<br />\n五個訴求都好重要 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但只有雙普選 先係對付政府</span></span></span> 係民主運動嘅第一步<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd10cc2995d2a5b8b8f5d6a7d2c0ce3c7b6f05cb","tid":1596603,"uid":158672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"886d6c68a0688f99851ac547919eb1b5a609999f","tid":1596603,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"行動post求推<br />\n<br />\n【負皮我＝AntiChinazi】【929 SOGO見】 929 行動整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1596268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1596268</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f66ba5ed5138e86ce191e3e933a46a9ec3da657","tid":1596603,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AV2aCQ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2